@base = http://localhost:8086
@contentType = application/json

### 健康检查
GET {{base}}/actuator/health

### 创建账户 A
POST {{base}}/api/v1/accounts
Content-Type: {{contentType}}

{
  "accountNumber": "A10001",
  "ownerName": "Alice",
  "email": "alice@example.com",
  "initialBalance": 5000,
  "currency": "AUD"
}

### 创建账户 B
POST {{base}}/api/v1/accounts
Content-Type: {{contentType}}

{
  "accountNumber": "B20001",
  "ownerName": "Bob",
  "email": "bob@example.com",
  "initialBalance": 1000,
  "currency": "AUD"
}

### 查询账户 A
GET {{base}}/api/v1/accounts/A10001

### 查询账户 B
GET {{base}}/api/v1/accounts/B20001

### 发起支付 (A -> B)
POST http://localhost:8086/api/v1/payments
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "idempotencyKey": "idem-1",
  "sourceAccount": "A10001",
  "destinationAccount": "B20001",
  "amount": 120.50,
  "currency": "AUD"
}


### 根据交易号查询支付 (把 {trxRef} 替换为上一步响应里的 transactionRef)
GET {{base}}/api/v1/payments/{trxRef}

### 退款 (把 {trxRef} 替换为上一步的 transactionRef)
POST {{base}}/api/v1/payments/{trxRef}/refund
Content-Type: {{contentType}}

{
  "idempotencyKey": "refund-1",
  "reason": "customer_request"
}

### 幂等性检查：同一个 idempotencyKey 再发一次，应该返回相同的 transactionRef
POST http://localhost:8086/api/v1/payments
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "idempotencyKey": "idem-1",
  "sourceAccount": "A10001",
  "destinationAccount": "B20001",
  "amount": 120.50,
  "currency": "AUD"
}

### 查询交易（把 {trxRef} 替换为上一步/你现在拿到的值）
GET http://localhost:8086/api/v1/payments/{trxRef}

### 发起退款
POST http://localhost:8086/api/v1/payments/{trxRef}/refund
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "idempotencyKey": "refund-1",
  "reason": "customer_request",
  "callbackUrl": "http://localhost:9999/callback"
}
